(8, 'How to Build an Auction Site like eBay using WordPress', 'How-to-Build-an-Auction-Site-like-eBay-using-WordPress', '996.jpg', 'two', 'video', 'publish', 'no', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">Do you want to build an auction site like eBay using WordPress? An auction website allow users to bid on products to purchase them. This allows you to maximize profits while selling unique products. In this article, we will show you how to easily build an auction site like eBay using WordPress without any technical skills.</span></p><p><br></p><h4 style=\"color: rgb(255, 98, 0); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial; font-weight: 700 !important; text-decoration: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.6em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">What Do You Need to Build an Auction Site Using WordPress?</h4><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">You will need the following things to make your own auction site like eBay using WordPress.</p><ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">A domain name (This will be your website’s name that people will type to find your site e.g. wpbeginner.com)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">A web hosting account (This is where your website’s files are stored)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">SSL Certificate (You need this to recieve online payments)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">An ecommerce addon (This will turn your website into an ecommerce platform)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">An auctions addon (This will add auction features to your website)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">Your undivided attention for 40 mins</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Yes, you can start your own auction site in 40 minutes, and we will walk you through the whole process, step by step.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">In this tutorial, we will cover the following:</p><ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">How to get a domain name for free</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">How to choose the best website hosting</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">Install WordPress and set up your ecommerce addon</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">Install and set up auctions addon</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">Add and manage auctions</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; font-size: 15px; list-style-type: square;\">Resources to learn WordPress and grow your business</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">That being said, let’s get started.</p><h4 style=\"color: rgb(255, 98, 0); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial; font-weight: 700 !important; text-decoration: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.6em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Step 1. The Right Setup</h4><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">First, you need to make sure that you are using the right<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/how-to-choose-the-best-website-builder/\" title=\"How to Choose the Best Website Builder in 2018 (Compared)\" style=\"color: rgb(234, 106, 27); text-decoration: none;\">website platform</a>, and since you’re on this article, you won’t be making the mistake that others do.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">There are two types of WordPress software, so it’s easy for beginners to get confused. First, there is WordPress.com which is a hosting platform, and then you have WordPress.org also known as self-hosted WordPress.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">We recommend using self-hosted WordPress.org because it gives you access to all WordPress features out of the box. For comparison, see the difference between<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/self-hosted-wordpress-org-vs-free-wordpress-com-infograph/\" title=\"WordPress.com vs WordPress.org – Which is Better? (Comparison Chart)\" style=\"color: rgb(234, 106, 27); text-decoration: none;\">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a>.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">First, you will need a<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/whats-the-difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-explained/\" title=\"What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting (Explained)\" style=\"color: rgb(234, 106, 27); text-decoration: none;\">domain name and a web hosting</a><span>&nbsp;</span>account. But you cannot sign up with just any web hosting company. You will need a hosting provider that specializes in<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/best-woocommerce-hosting/\" title=\"Best WooCommerce Hosting in 2018 (Reviews &amp; Performance Tests)\" style=\"color: rgb(234, 106, 27); text-decoration: none;\">WooCommerce hosting</a><span>&nbsp;</span>because this is the software you’ll be using as your e-commerce platform.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Usually, a domain name costs $14.99/year, web hosting 7.99/month, and SSL certificate 69.99/year.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Now, this is a lot of money if you are just starting out.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Fortunately,<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/refer/bluehost-ecommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost Ecommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(234, 106, 27); text-decoration: none;\">Bluehost</a>, an officially recommended WordPress and WooCommerce hosting provider has agreed to offer our users a free domain + free SSL and discount on their cloud WordPress hosting.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Basically, you can get started for $6.95 / month.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Once you have purchased the hosting, then follow our step by step tutorial on<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-start-an-online-store/\" title=\"How to Start an Online Store in 2018 (Step by Step)\" style=\"color: rgb(234, 106, 27); text-decoration: none;\">how to start an online store</a><span>&nbsp;</span>for complete setup instructions.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">You would now have a WordPress website with WooCommerce installed on it. By default, WooCommerce doesn’t allow you to add products for auction on your website.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Let’s change this by installing an auctions addon for WooCommerce.</p><h4 style=\"color: rgb(255, 98, 0); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial; font-weight: 700 !important; text-decoration: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.6em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Step 2. Turn Your Ecommerce Store into an Auctions Site</h4><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">First, you need to install and activate the<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-auctions/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"YITH WooCommerce Auctions\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(234, 106, 27); text-decoration: none;\">YITH WooCommerce Auctions</a><span>&nbsp;</span>plugin. For more details, see our step by step guide on<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners/\" title=\"Step by Step Guide to Install a WordPress Plugin for Beginners\" style=\"color: rgb(234, 106, 27); text-decoration: none;\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">YITH WooCommerce Auctions is a paid plugin and a single site license will cost you 81 Euros. This gives you access to the plugin downloads, documentation, and 1 year of support and updates.</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Upon activation, you need to visit<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>YITH Plugins » License Activation</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>page to enter your license key. You can find this information under your account on plugin’s website.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: proxima-nova, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p>', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LO4YTml3IAQ', '2020-07-06', '2020-07-06 03:53:19', '2020-07-06 03:53:19'),
